OL,7,FHundreds of Presbyterian ministers and
OL,8,Felders will meet later to agree new
OL,9,Fmeasures on safeguarding.
OL,11,FThe special General Assembly comes
OL,12,Fafter the church announced that
OL,13,Fsignificant failings had been found in
OL,14,Fcentral safeguarding functions.
