OL,7,FFormer Presbyterian moderator Rev
OL,8,FTrevor Gribben stood down earlier this
OL,9,Fyear after a review found "serious and
OL,10,Fsignificant failings" in central
OL,11,Fsafeguarding functions from 2009 to
OL,12,F2022.Rev Richard Murray resumed the
OL,13,Foffice of Moderator and called a
OL,14,Fspecial General Assembly, a rare event
OL,15,Ffor the church, with just a handful
OL,16,Fcalled in recent decades.
