OL,3,CPresbyterians to hold special General
OL,4,CAssembly to agree measures on
OL,5,Csafeguarding
OL,7,FOn Thursday, up to 900 ministers and
OL,8,Felders from the 540 congregations
OL,9,Facross the island of Ireland will
OL,10,Ftravel to Belfast to take part in
OL,11,Fprayers and reflection at the
OL,12,Fheadquarters of the church at Assembly
OL,13,FBuildings.
OL,15,FIn the afternoon they are expected to
OL,16,Fdebate and vote to agree new measures
OL,17,Frelating to safeguarding and other
OL,18,Frelated matters in proceedings open to
OL,19,Fthe public and media.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
