OL,3,CPresbyterians to hold special General
OL,4,CAssembly to agree measures on
OL,5,Csafeguarding
OL,7,FProposals include to establish a new
OL,8,FSafeguarding Department and
OL,9,Fpotentially separate the roles of
OL,10,Fclerk of the General Assembly and
OL,11,Fgeneral secretary of the church.
OL,13,FActing clerk of the General Assembly,
OL,14,FRev David Allen, said the church
OL,15,Ffamily come together as they find
OL,16,Fthemselves "in a place of shame and
OL,17,Fhumility as a result of our central
OL,18,Fsafeguarding failings". He said it
OL,19,Fwill be a "significant and humbling
OL,20,Fevent".
OL,26,@xD@LOUzD@VO]{D@KOU|D@FO]
