OL,7,F"The report of our General Council
OL,8,Fthat will be discussed by the General
OL,9,FAssembly, along with its resolutions
OL,10,Fto be voted on, states that our
OL,11,Ffailings over a 13-year period 'has
OL,12,Fresulted in some people being harmed
OL,13,Fby actions and inactions in the name
OL,14,Fof the denomination, and some people
OL,15,Fbeing placed at unnecessary risk'," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@cO]
