OL,7,F"It also states that '(t)his is a
OL,8,Fshameful position for part of the
OL,9,FChurch of Jesus Christ to be in'."He
OL,10,Fadded: "As Dr Murray said in his
OL,11,Fletter to ministers announcing the
OL,12,FGeneral Assembly, it is important that
OL,13,Fwe 'come together as a family before
OL,14,FGod to grieve and lament for our
OL,15,Ffailings. At the same time, we also
OL,16,Fwant to be particularly mindful of
OL,17,Fthose who have been harmed as a result
OL,18,Fof our central failings'."
