OL,5,Csafeguarding
OL,7,FHe said the proposals to be brought
OL,8,Fare aimed to "elevate significantly
OL,9,Fthe position of safeguarding" within
OL,10,Fthe church.
OL,12,F"This includes a proposal to establish
OL,13,Fa new Safeguarding Department, along
OL,14,Fwith the effective resourcing of
OL,15,Fsafeguarding centrally, and at an
OL,16,Fappropriate time, a full, independent
OL,17,Fexternal review of safeguarding in
OL,18,FPCI," he said.
