OL,5,Csafeguarding
OL,7,F"This will be in addition to the
OL,8,FSafeguarding Board for Northern
OL,9,FIreland's section 12 audit process,
OL,10,Fwhich is currently being conducted by
OL,11,Fan independent external assessor.
OL,13,FThe General Assembly will also be
OL,14,Fasked to establish a task group that
OL,15,Fwill look at governance, culture and
OL,16,Fintegrity.
