OL,7,F"The role of clerk of the General
OL,8,FAssembly and general secretary of the
OL,9,FPresbyterian Church in Ireland and the
OL,10,Fpossible separation of these roles,
OL,11,Fwill be considered by Members of
OL,12,FAssembly, as will the role of the
OL,13,Fincoming Moderator for 2026-2027 and
OL,14,Fthe format of next year's General
OL,15,FAssembly.
OL,17,F"An update on recent engagement with
OL,18,Fthe Charity Commission for Northern
OL,19,FIreland will also form part of our
OL,20,Fproceedings."
